text: Stagecoach to Fury is a 1956 American western movie directed by William F. Claxton and starring Forrest Tucker, Mari Blanchard, Wallace Ford, Paul Fix, Wright King, Ellen Corby, Rayford Barnes. It was distributed by 20th Century Fox. ==Other websites== * Category:1956 movies Category:1950s Western (genre) movies Category:American Western (genre) movies Category:Movies directed by William F.
